	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My small thrust inspired game is mostly complete.  Can't think of anything major to add to it at the moment, except for the horrible lack of a title.  Five levels with a mostly introductory first level and a few additional enemies.  It's not much on presentation or audio but I think it's reasonably playable.  What do you think?
<br />
<br />There was a randomly occurring bug (good god I hate these) where it would glitch on loading a strip of graphics in the level, but I think I've patched that up.
<br />
<br /><a href="http://smkdan.eludevisibility.org/other/rom.zip" class="postlink">http://smkdan.eludevisibility.org/other/rom.zip</a>
<br />
<br />Thanks for reading

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


